<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Interactive Image Gallery</title>
  <!-- Include jQuery from CDN -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f0f0f0;
    }
    .filter-buttons {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .filter-buttons button {
      background: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      margin: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .filter-buttons button:hover {
      background: #2980b9;
    }
    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      position: relative;
      width: 200px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
    .img-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      color: #fff;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5px 0;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover .img-overlay {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="filter-buttons">
    <button data-filter="all">All</button>
    <button data-filter="nature">Nature</button>
    <button data-filter="animals">Animals</button>
    <button data-filter="architecture">Architecture</button>
  </div>

  <div class="gallery">
    <!-- Nature images -->
    <div class="gallery-item nature">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Nature 1">
      <div class="img-overlay">Nature 1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-item nature">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Nature 2">
      <div class="img-overlay">Nature 2</div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Animals images -->
    <div class="gallery-item animals">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Animal 1">
      <div class="img-overlay">Animal 1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-item animals">
      <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ38Ns-CVTDefJzIOyf7qTAbQ0M09CRhV1oQA&s" alt="Animal 2">
      <div class="img-overlay">Animal 2</div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Architecture images -->
    <div class="gallery-item architecture">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Architecture 1">
      <div class="img-overlay">Architecture 1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-item architecture">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Architecture 2">
      <div class="img-overlay">Architecture 2</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
      $('.filter-buttons button').on('click', function() {
        var filterValue = $(this).attr('data-filter');
        if(filterValue === 'all'){
          $('.gallery-item').fadeIn(200);
        } else {
          $('.gallery-item').each(function() {
            // Check if the item has the category class
            if($(this).hasClass(filterValue)) {
              $(this).fadeIn(200);
            } else {
              $(this).fadeOut(50);
            }
          });
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
